# Generated tests are kept under .ai-workspace/generated-tests/<repo_id>/.
# We DO track these — they ship as reproducible demo artifacts so a
# reviewer cloning the repo sees an example of what `verify generate`
# produces against petclinic. New entries are added by `verify generate`
# and should be committed alongside other source changes.
